:::tip

Versioned sidebar files are, like standard sidebar files, relative to the content root for the given version — so for the example above, your versioned sidebar file may look like:

```json
{
  "sidebar": [
    {
      "type": "autogenerated",
      "dirName": "."
    }
  ]
}
```

or for a manual sidebar:

```json
{
  "sidebar": [
    {
      "type": "doc",
      "id": "new",
      "label": "New"
    }
  ]
}
```

:::

